# GitHub Access Report Backend - Environment Variables
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN - Personal Access Token for GitHub API authentication (required)
#   Must have scopes: read:org, repo (or full control of private repositories)
#   Example: GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GITHUB_TOKEN=

# GITHUB_ORG - Default GitHub organization or username to scan (optional)
#   IMPORTANT: Use the organization/user name only, NOT a full URL.
#   Correct:   GITHUB_ORG=myorg
#   Incorrect: GITHUB_ORG=https://github.com/myorg
#   If a full URL is accidentally provided, the app will attempt to extract the name automatically.
GITHUB_ORG=
